SELECT
        VARCHAR(GE10VALCOM) AS GE10VALCOM_STRING
FROM
	GXGEDTA.GET010
WHERE
	GE10ORICOD = 600
	AND GE10DESCOD = 840
	AND GE10FH >= '$vFechaConsultaAnterior$ 23:59:59'
	AND GE10FH < '$vFechaConsulta$ 23:59:59'
ORDER BY
	GE10FH DESC
